   "type": "text",
   "x": 40,
   "y": 372,
   "width": 1726.48,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "Only a direct mention in #alpha-ai reaches the gateway; DMs, other channels, and un-mentioned messages get no response. The gateway binds loopback 18789 and runs as a user service with linger, so it survives logout, and the resolver turns a name into a real Discord mention.",
   "originalText": "Only a direct mention in #alpha-ai reaches the gateway; DMs, other channels, and un-mentioned messages get no response. The gateway binds loopback 18789 and runs as a user service with linger, so it survives logout, and the resolver turns a name into a real Discord mention.",
